{
  "stem": "19055.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 291.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm thinking, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] let's say, in the years from '39 to 1940, 1941, that period.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the, the government, the cabinet, the administration was anti-Semitic in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jewish laws were created-- the first Jewish law, the second Jewish law.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each one brought more and more restrictions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just to give you an example, there was a law that Jews couldn't bear guns.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father sold guns and shotguns and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would take it away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then was another law that Jews couldn't sell wine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my father couldn't sell any more wine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So there was a gradual decrease in your livelihood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a gradual restriction in your lifestyle and, and, and lives through these laws.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Jews couldn't have a public service.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They couldn't be employed by public.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then came the worst, of course, it was the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the so-called clean race law, that a Jewish man, a Jewish person, could not have sexual relation with a Christian.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this was terribly serially punishable if it happened, it occurred, or if they charged somebody with this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So these laws centrally came from Budapest in a country which, at one time, was extremely liberal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father always mentioned the good old times during Kaiser Franz Joseph and when the monarchy was quite liberal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Jews flourished at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] What happened exactly that Horthy went along on the-- the governor of the country-- he went along with all these laws, which were brought by, by his anti-Semitic cabinet.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And eventually, he was himself deposed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, and the government was taken over by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he was under house arrest himself.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
